mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: SPECIAL FEATURES "Here's a Sample Program for a One Night Stand", "Homes for Square Dancing, Part III", "Square Dance Workshops Feature of National Convention", "A Square Dance Mardi Gras", "America's Gain", "Techniques in Teaching Fundamentals", and "County Council Promotes Florida Dancing". This edition also includes the the regular features entitled "Square Dance Date Book", "From the Floor", "As I See It", "Square Dance Picture", "Chuck Jones' Note Book", "Style Series: Triple Allemande", "Round the Outside Ring", "Caller of the Month: Lou Hughes", "Paging the Roundancers: Vince and Marge Belgarbo", "On the Record", and "Style Series: Left Square Through".
